---
title: Jumpin’ Jack Chicken Bowls with Rice, Sour Cream & Lime
description: We’ve said it before, and we’ll say it again: Everything’s better in a bowl! The customizable combo of carbs, proteins, veggies, and delicious condiments simply can’t be denied. True to form, this rendition is fully loaded with fluffy rice, saucy spiced chicken, melty pepper jack cheese, tangy sour cream, and fresh scallions. One bite will have you totally bowled over.
